name: Bong O Clock
description: Haven't put out any music under the name Bong City and almost two years now since the 'Lost in the Club' EP. H=N has been a great way for me to finally be recognized for my niche style of music an art. it's been a big motivation to me to be creative again since losing my youtube partnership for failing to meet guidelines of watch time and they still run ads on my work! it's wild. i have been making art for 20 plus years now and I'm finally starting to make a little bit of money and I just want to thank you all for letting me part of this community. blaze the fuck up. big 420 style. shout out to all of you that have been supporting my broke ass!
